Class Vehiculo

java.lang.Object
Transporte.Vehiculo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sprites
Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Vehiculo extends Object implements Sprites
Clase abstracta que representa un vehículo. Implementa la interfaz Sprites.
